g.title: Literal_2
g.text: Represents information about a digital photo.

g.title: Literal_4
g.text: Short description of the picture's content.

g.title: Literal_6
g.text: Long description of the picture's content.

g.title: Literal_10
g.text: The creation datetime in W3CDTF profile of ISO 8601.

g.title: Literal_12
g.text: The location where the photo was taken.

g.title: Literal_14
g.text: Either the title of the photo series or a URI to the series.

g.title: Literal_16
g.text: Unique identifier for the creator or within the series.

g.title: Literal_18
g.text: Represents technical information about a digital photo.

g.title: Literal_20
g.text: The exact camera name and model or a URI.

g.title: Literal_22
g.text: Technical details about this specific photo (e.g. ISO value).

g.title: Literal_24
g.text: The exact lens name and model or a URI.
